user.biography:
🍸Cocktail Enthusiast
📍Denver, Colorado
🥂Poring @corinnedenver 
💛Livin life through rose colored lenses & high spirits

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ash Lewis in Corinne with @samslammyau, and @corinnedenver. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text:
When I accepted a position at a restaurant in a hotel in denver, little did I know how much I’d love it and who I’d meet. *so cliche* but this phrase has never hit so hard… “everything happens for a reason”

Moving to denver, I had very different reasons and expectations… going through heartbreak (over a job) I was so down and out… esp after a year like 2020

Working at Corinne, and joining this restaurant family has given me the joy I have been waiting for. I am so fucking lucky to have met this human, who has truly lifted me up, and inspires me on the daily… I am BEYOND thankful for this job opportunity but even more thankful for the people who have entered my life with it.

@samslammyau thank you for tying the room together 🥰
@corinnedenver thank you for allowing me to work at your amazing venue, I’m honored. 
📸 my bff @rachontherox 

#restaurant #restaurantfamily #family #industry #bartender #bartenders #denver #denverfoodie #mixology #craftcocktails #love #lovenote #restaurants #restaurantlife #restaurantbar #corinne #corinnedenver #lemeridian #denverbars #denverrestaurants #inspo #girlyinspo #moving #denvercocktail

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ash Lewis in Corinne with @liquor, @hendricksgin, @denverwestword, @stgermaindrinks, @garnishcraftcocktails, @visitdenver, @thirsty, @worldclassus, @milehighandhungry, @rootbitters, @denverfoodscene, @apartment_bartender, @thirsty_magazine, @barprints, @mix_o_logic, @artofdrinks, @corinnedenver, @craftedmixology, @teddysinthemixx, and @world.of.mixologists. May be an image of drink and indoor.

node.text:
Made this fun little number last night. 

1.5 oz Hendricks @hendricksgin 
.25 oz St Germain @stgermaindrinks stgermaindrinks 
.75 oz lime
.5 oz simple
Muddled cucumber 

So refreshing and light! Roll through Corinne and see me! 

📍 @corinnedenver

I don’t usually do mixers but… 

Pina Me Crazy

2 oz Tequila @tequilacurado 
2oz Pina Colada Mix @craftedbrandco 
.25oz Asian Pear Shrub @craftedbrandco 
.5oz Lime Juice

Method

Add all ingredients to an iced shaker. Shake and pour.
Garnish with a banana slice

Cheers!

Glassware @riedel_official

3/4 ounce simple syrup
1/2 ounce heavy cream
1/2 ounce pressed lemon juice
1/2 ounce pressed lime juice
3 dashes orange flower water
1 fresh egg white
Club soda, to top
